folder: Central Park West & 95th Street, Manhattan, NY
text:
Central Park West, at and adjoining the N.W. corner of 95th Street. No. 1 West 95th Street, on the corner, and 352-355 Central Park West, adjoining it, will remain when the Scotch Presbyterian Chapel at 3 West 95th Street, together with the adjoining houses, is demolished in September to make room for a sixteen-story apartment building.

May 31, 1928.

P. L. Sperr.
